Everything that's unlocked past the 50% speed boost and sliders feels awful for how much grinding is put into them. The wave progression also feels horrible since enemies begin to turn into damage sponges by wave 10, while also increasing in numbers as well. As a joke game to play when bored, it's alright, but it sure becomes quite time consuming and boring. Even the power ups begin to scale horribly in the later waves, making them risky to grab with enemies firing at you while animation locked.
